Class MapCreate<K,V>

  • Object
    • MapCreate<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - identifier (key)-type
    V - value-type

    public class MapCreate<K,V>
extends Object
    A tree map that creates a new item, if it doesn't already exist upon a get operation.

    Owen Feehan
